Require Import extac.

Require Import List.

Set Implicit Arguments.
Unset Strict Implicit.

Module Type MAP_DOMAIN.

  Parameter A : Set.

  Axiom beq : A → A → bool.

  Axiom blt : A → A → bool.

  Axiom beq_true_eq : ∀ a a' : A,
    beq a a' = true → a = a'.

  Axiom beq_false_neq : ∀ a a' : A,
    beq a a' = false → a ≠ a'.

  Axiom eq_beq_true : ∀ a a' : A,
    a = a' → beq a a' = true.

  Axiom neq_beq_false : ∀ a a' : A,
    a ≠ a' → beq a a' = false.

  Axiom blt_trans : ∀ a a' a'' : A,
    blt a a' = true → blt a' a'' = true → blt a a'' = true.

  Axiom blt_irrefl : ∀ a : A,
    blt a a = false.

  Axiom blt_asym : ∀ a b : A,
    blt a b = true → blt b a = false.

  Axiom blt_beq_dec : ∀ a b : A,
    {blt a b = true} + {beq a b = true} + {blt b a = true}.

End MAP_DOMAIN.

Module Type MAP_RANGE.

  Parameter B : Type.

End MAP_RANGE.

Module MapFun (Domain : MAP_DOMAIN) (Range : MAP_RANGE).

Import Domain.

Import Range.

Lemma A_exclude_middle:
  ∀ (a b: A),
    a = b ∨ a ≠ b.
Proof.
  intros.
  remember(beq a b) as H.
  destruct H.
  apply eq_sym in HeqH.
  apply beq_true_eq in HeqH.
  left; auto.
  apply eq_sym in HeqH.
  apply beq_false_neq in HeqH.
  right; auto.
Qed.








Lemma beq_dec : ∀ a a' : A, {beq a a' = true} + {beq a a' = false}.
Proof.
  intros; destruct (beq a a'); [left | right]; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma eq_dec : ∀ a a' : A, {a = a'} + {a ≠ a'}.
Proof.
  intros; destruct (beq_dec a a'); [left | right].
  apply beq_true_eq; trivial.
  apply beq_false_neq; trivial.
Qed.

Ltac beq_case_tac x y :=
  let Hb := fresh "Hb" in
    (destruct (beq_dec x y) as [Hb | Hb]; trivial).

Lemma beq_sym : ∀ a a' b,
  beq a a' = b → beq a' a = b.
Proof.
  intros m n b H.
  destruct b.
    apply eq_beq_true.
    apply sym_eq.
    apply beq_true_eq; trivial.
  apply neq_beq_false.
  apply sym_not_eq.
  apply beq_false_neq; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma beq_refl : ∀ a, beq a a = true.
Proof.
  intro m.
  apply eq_beq_true; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma beq_trans : ∀ a a' a'' b, beq a a' = true
  → beq a' a'' = b
  → beq a a'' = b.
Proof.
  intros m n k b H1 H2.
  assert (m = n).
    apply beq_true_eq; trivial.
  subst m.
  destruct b.
    apply eq_beq_true.
    apply beq_true_eq; trivial.
  apply neq_beq_false.
  apply beq_false_neq; trivial.
Qed.

Ltac beq_simpl_tac :=
  match goal with

    
    | [H : beq ?x ?y = ?f
      |- context [(beq ?x ?y)]] ⇒
       rewrite H; beq_simpl_tac
    | [H : beq ?x ?y = ?f,
       H0 : context [(beq ?x ?y)] |- _ ] ⇒
       rewrite H in H0; beq_simpl_tac

    
    | [ |- context [(beq ?x ?x)] ] ⇒
      rewrite (@beq_refl x); beq_simpl_tac
    | [H : context [(beq ?x ?x)] |- _ ] ⇒
      rewrite (@beq_refl x) in H; beq_simpl_tac

    
    | [ H : beq ?x ?y = ?b
        |- context [(beq ?y ?x)] ] ⇒
      rewrite (@beq_sym x y b H); beq_simpl_tac
    | [H : beq ?x ?y = ?b,
       H0 : context [(beq ?y ?x)] |- _ ] ⇒
      rewrite (@beq_sym x y b H) in H0; beq_simpl_tac

    
    | [ H : ?x ≠ ?y |- context [(beq ?x ?y)] ] ⇒
      rewrite (neq_beq_false H); beq_simpl_tac
    | [ H : ?x ≠ ?y,
        H0 : context [(beq ?x ?y)] |- _ ] ⇒
      rewrite (neq_beq_false H) in H0; beq_simpl_tac
    | [ H : ?x ≠ ?y |- context [(beq ?y ?x)] ] ⇒
      rewrite (beq_sym (neq_beq_false H)); beq_simpl_tac
    | [ H : ?x ≠ ?y,
        H0 : context [(beq ?y ?x)] |- _ ] ⇒
      rewrite (beq_sym (neq_beq_false H)) in H0; beq_simpl_tac

    
    | [ H : (beq ?x ?y = false) |- ?x ≠ ?y ] ⇒
      apply (beq_false_neq H); beq_simpl_tac
    | [ H : (beq ?x ?y = false) |- ?y ≠ ?x ] ⇒
      apply (beq_false_neq (beq_sym H)); beq_simpl_tac

    
    
    
    
    
        
    | [H : ?x = ?x |- _ ] ⇒ clear H; beq_simpl_tac
    | [H : true = false |- _ ] ⇒ discriminate H
    | [H : false = true |- _ ] ⇒ discriminate H

    | [|- true = true ] ⇒ trivial
    | [|- false = false ] ⇒ trivial

    | [|- context [beq ?x ?y] ] ⇒ simpl; trivial
    | [ H: context [beq ?x ?y] |- _ ] ⇒ simpl in H

    | _ ⇒ idtac
  end.


Tactic Notation "beq" "simpl" := beq_simpl_tac.

Ltac beq_rewrite_tac H :=
  match type of H with
    | beq ?a ?b = true ⇒
      match goal with
        | [ |- context [(?a)]] ⇒
          rewrite (@beq_true_eq a b H)
        | [ |- context [(?b)]] ⇒
          rewrite <- (@beq_true_eq a b H)
      end
    | _ ⇒ fail
  end.

Tactic Notation "beq" "rewrite" constr(t) := beq_rewrite_tac t.

Ltac beq_rewriteH_tac H H' :=
  match type of H with
    | beq ?a ?b = true ⇒
      match type of H' with
        | context [(?a)] ⇒
          rewrite (@beq_true_eq a b H) in H'
        | context [(?b)] ⇒
          rewrite <- (@beq_true_eq a b H) in H'
      end
    | _ ⇒ fail
  end.

Tactic Notation "beq" "rewrite" constr(t) "in" hyp(H) := beq_rewriteH_tac t H.

Section Test.
  Variables a b a' : A.
  Goal beq a b = true → beq a a' = true → False.
    intros.
    beq_rewriteH_tac H0 H.
  Abort.
End Test.

Lemma blt_dec : ∀ a b,
  {blt a b = true} + {blt a b = false}.
Proof.
  intros a b.
  destruct (blt a b); [left | right]; trivial.
Qed.


Lemma blt_t_beq_f :
  ∀ m n, blt m n = true
    → beq m n = false.
Proof.
  intros m n H.
  beq_case_tac m n.
  rewrite (beq_true_eq Hb) in H.
  rewrite (blt_irrefl) in H.
  discriminate.
Qed.

Lemma bgt_t_beq_f :
  ∀ m n, blt n m = true
    → beq m n = false.
Proof.
  intros m n H.
  apply beq_sym.
  apply blt_t_beq_f.
  trivial.
Qed.

Lemma beq_t_blt_f :
  ∀ m n, beq m n = true
    → blt m n = false.
Proof.
  intros m n H.
  rewrite (beq_true_eq H).
  apply blt_irrefl.
Qed.

Lemma beq_t_bgt_f :
  ∀ m n, beq m n = true
    → blt n m = false.
Proof.
  intros m n H.
  rewrite (beq_true_eq H).
  apply blt_irrefl.
Qed.

Lemma blt_beq_blt : ∀ a a',
  blt a a' = false → beq a a' = false → blt a' a = true.
Proof.
  intros a a' H1 H2.
  destruct (blt_beq_dec a a') as [[H3 | H4] | H5].
      rewrite H3 in H1.
      discriminate.
    rewrite H2 in H4.
    discriminate.
  trivial.
Qed.

Ltac blt_simpl_tac :=
  match goal with
    
    | [H : blt ?x ?y = ?f
      |- context [(blt ?x ?y)]] ⇒
       rewrite H; blt_simpl_tac
    | [H : blt ?x ?y = ?f,
       H0 : context [(blt ?x ?y)]
      |- _ ] ⇒
       rewrite H in H0; blt_simpl_tac
         
    
    | [H : blt ?x ?y = true
      |- context[(beq ?x ?y)]] ⇒
      rewrite (blt_t_beq_f H); blt_simpl_tac
    | [H : blt ?x ?y = true,
       H0 : context[(beq ?x ?y)] |- _ ] ⇒
      rewrite (blt_t_beq_f H) in H0; blt_simpl_tac
     
    
    | [H : blt ?y ?x = true
      |- context[(beq ?x ?y)]] ⇒
      rewrite (bgt_t_beq_f H); blt_simpl_tac
    | [H : blt ?y ?x = true,
       H0 : context[(beq ?x ?y)] |- _ ] ⇒
      rewrite (bgt_t_beq_f H) in H0; blt_simpl_tac
         
    
    | [H : beq ?y ?x = true
      |- context[(blt ?x ?y)]] ⇒
      rewrite (beq_t_blt_f H); blt_simpl_tac
    | [H : beq ?y ?x = true,
       H0 : context[(blt ?x ?y)] |- _ ] ⇒
      rewrite (beq_t_blt_f H) in H0; blt_simpl_tac
         
    
    | [H : beq ?y ?x = true
      |- context[(blt ?y ?x)]] ⇒
      rewrite (beq_t_bgt_f H); blt_simpl_tac
    | [H : beq ?y ?x = true,
       H0 : context[(blt ?y ?x)] |- _ ] ⇒
      rewrite (beq_t_bgt_f H) in H0; blt_simpl_tac

    
    | [ |- context [blt ?x ?x]] ⇒
      rewrite (@blt_irrefl x); blt_simpl_tac
    | [H : context [blt ?x ?x] |- _ ] ⇒
      rewrite (@blt_irrefl x) in H; blt_simpl_tac

    
    | [H : blt ?x ?y = true
      |- context [blt ?y ?x]] ⇒
      rewrite (blt_asym x y H); blt_simpl_tac
    | [H : blt ?x ?y = true,
       H0 : context [blt ?y ?x] |- _ ] ⇒
      rewrite (blt_asym x y H) in H0; blt_simpl_tac

    
    | [H : blt ?x ?y = false,
       H1 : beq ?x ?y = false
      |- context [blt ?y ?x]] ⇒
      apply (blt_beq_blt H H1); blt_simpl_tac
    | [H : blt ?x ?y = false,
       H1 : beq ?y ?x = false
      |- context [blt ?y ?x]] ⇒
      apply (blt_beq_blt H (beq_sym H1)); blt_simpl_tac

    | [H : ?x = ?x |- _ ] ⇒ clear H; blt_simpl_tac
    | [H : true = false |- _ ] ⇒ discriminate H
    | [H : false = true |- _ ] ⇒ discriminate H
    | _ ⇒ idtac
  end.

Ltac blt_dec_tac x y :=
  let Hb := fresh "Hb" in
    (destruct (blt_dec x y) as [Hb | Hb]; blt_simpl_tac).

Definition of map

Definition rlist := list (prod A B).

Fixpoint lb (a : A) (rl : rlist) {struct rl} : Prop :=
  match rl with
    | nil ⇒ True
    | (a', b') :: rl' ⇒ (blt a a' = true) ∧ (lb a rl')
  end.

Lemma lb_trans :
  ∀ rl a1 a2, lb a2 rl → blt a1 a2 = true → lb a1 rl.
Proof.
  unfold lb.
  induction rl as [ | (a, b) rl' IHrl' ]; fold lb in *; trivial.
  intros a1 a2 [H1 H2] H.
  split.
  apply blt_trans with a2; trivial.
  apply (IHrl' a1 a2); trivial.
Qed.

Fixpoint is_orderset (rl : rlist) : Prop :=
  match rl with
    | nil ⇒ True
    | (a', b') :: rl' ⇒ (lb a' rl') ∧ (is_orderset rl')
  end.

map

Inductive listset :=
  | listset_con : ∀ lst : rlist,
                 is_orderset lst → listset.

Definition map := listset.

Definition lst (m : listset) := let (lst, _) := m in lst.

Definition prf (m : listset) :=
  let (lst, prf) as m return (is_orderset (lst m))
    := m in prf.

Fixpoint domain' (rl: rlist) {struct rl} :(set A) :=
  match rl with
    | nil ⇒ empty_set A
    | (a', b') :: rl' ⇒ set_add eq_dec a' (domain' rl')
  end.

Definition domain (m : map) (a : A) := domain' (lst m).

Fixpoint get' (rl : rlist) (a : A) {struct rl} : option B :=
  match rl with
    | nil ⇒ None
    | (a', b') :: rl' ⇒
        match (beq a a') with
          | true ⇒ Some b'
          | false ⇒ get' rl' a
        end
  end.

Lemma lb_notin :
  ∀ rl a, lb a rl → get' rl a = None.
Proof.
  unfold get', lb.
  induction rl as [|(a', b') rl' IHrl']; trivial.
  intros a [H1 H2].
  destruct (eq_dec a a') as [Heq | Hneq].
    subst a'.
    rewrite (@blt_irrefl a) in H1.
    discriminate.
  beq_simpl_tac.
  apply IHrl'.
  apply H2.
Qed.

Lemma in_notlb :
  ∀ rl a b, get' rl a = Some b → ¬ lb a rl.
Proof.
  unfold not;intros.
  rewrite (lb_notin H0) in H.
  discriminate.
Qed.

Definition get (m : map) (a : A) := get' (lst m) a.

Lemma get_dec :
  ∀ (m : map) (a : A),
    {∃ b, get m a = Some b} + {get m a = None}.
Proof.
  intros m a.
  destruct (get m a).
  left.
  ∃ b.
  trivial.
  right; trivial.
Qed.


Definition emp' : rlist := nil.

Lemma is_orderset_emp' : is_orderset emp'.
Proof.
  red; apply I.
Qed.

Definition emp : map := listset_con is_orderset_emp'.

Lemma emp_sem :
  ∀ a : A, get emp a = None.
Proof.
  intros; unfold get, emp; trivial.
Qed.


Definition sig' (a : A) (b : B) := (a, b) :: nil.

Lemma is_orderset_sig' : ∀ a b, is_orderset (sig' a b).
Proof.
  unfold is_orderset, lb; intros; split; apply I.
Qed.

Definition sig (a : A) (b : B) :=
  @listset_con (sig' a b) (is_orderset_sig' a b).

Lemma sig_sem : ∀ (a a' : A) (b : B),
  get (sig a b) a' =
  match (beq a a') with
    | true ⇒ Some b
    | false ⇒ None
  end.
Proof.
  unfold get, sig, get', sig', lst. intros a a' b.
  destruct (eq_dec a a').
  rewrite e; trivial.
  rewrite (@neq_beq_false a a').
  rewrite (@neq_beq_false a' a).
  trivial.
  apply sym_not_eq; trivial.
  trivial.
Qed.

Require Import Coq.Logic.Classical_Prop.

Fixpoint set' (a : A) (b : B) (rl : rlist)
  {struct rl}: rlist :=
  match rl with
    | nil ⇒ (a, b) :: nil
    | (a', b') :: rl' ⇒
      match blt a a' with
        | true ⇒ (a, b) :: rl
        | false ⇒
          match beq a a' with
            | true ⇒ (a', b) :: rl'
            | false ⇒ (a', b') :: (set' a b rl')
          end

      end
  end.

Lemma get'_set' : ∀ rl a b,
  get' (set' a b rl) a = Some b.
Proof.
  intros rl a b.
  induction rl as [|(a', b') rl' IHrl'].
    simpl.
    beq_simpl_tac; trivial.
  simpl.
  destruct (blt_dec a a') as [Hblt | Hnblt].
    blt_simpl_tac.
    simpl.
    beq_simpl_tac.
    trivial.
  blt_simpl_tac.
  beq_case_tac a a'; beq_simpl_tac; simpl.
    rewrite Hb.
    trivial.
  beq_simpl_tac.
  trivial.
Qed.

Lemma get'_set'_neq : ∀ rl a a0 b,
  a ≠ a0 → get' (set' a b rl) a0 = get' rl a0.
Proof.
  intros rl a a0 b Hneq.
  induction rl as [|(a', b') rl' IHrl'].
    simpl.
    beq_simpl_tac.
    trivial.
  simpl.
  destruct (blt_dec a a') as [Hblt | Hnblt].
    rewrite Hblt.
    simpl.
    beq_simpl_tac.
    trivial.
  rewrite Hnblt.
  destruct (beq_dec a a') as [Hbeq | Hnbeq].
    rewrite Hbeq.
    simpl.
    beq_rewrite_tac Hbeq.
    beq_simpl_tac.
    trivial.
  rewrite Hnbeq.
  simpl.
  rewrite IHrl'.
  trivial.
Qed.

Lemma lb_set'_lt : ∀ rl a a0 b,
  lb a rl → blt a0 a = true → lb a0 (set' a b rl).
Proof.
  intros rl a a0 b Ha Hlta0.
  induction rl as [|(a', b') rl' IHrl'].
    simpl in ×.
    split; trivial.
  simpl in ×.
  destruct Ha as [Hlta Hlb].
  destruct (blt_dec a a') as [Hblt | Hnblt].
    rewrite Hblt.
    simpl.
    split; trivial.
    split.
      eapply blt_trans; eauto.
    eapply lb_trans; eauto.
  rewrite Hlta in Hnblt.
  discriminate.
Qed.

Lemma lb_set'_gt : ∀ rl a a0 b,
  lb a0 rl → blt a0 a = true → lb a0 (set' a b rl).
Proof.
  intros rl a a0 b Ha0 Hlta.
  induction rl as [|(a', b') rl' IHrl'].
    simpl in ×.
    split; trivial.
  simpl in ×.
  destruct Ha0 as [Hlta0 Hlb].
  destruct (blt_dec a a') as [Hblt | Hnblt].
    rewrite Hblt.
    simpl.
    split; trivial.
    split; trivial.
  rewrite Hnblt.
  destruct (beq_dec a a') as [Hbeq | Hnbeq].
    rewrite Hbeq.
    simpl.
    beq_rewrite_tac Hbeq.
    split; trivial.
  rewrite Hnbeq.
  simpl.
  split; trivial.
  apply (IHrl' Hlb).
Qed.

Lemma is_orderset_set' : ∀ rl : rlist,
  is_orderset rl → ∀ a b, is_orderset (set' a b rl).
Proof.
  intros rl Hrl a b.
  induction rl as [|(a', b') rl' IHrl'].
  split; trivial.
  simpl in ×.
  destruct Hrl as [Hlb Hrl'].
  destruct (blt_dec a a') as [Hblt | Hnblt].
    rewrite Hblt.
    simpl.
    split; split; trivial.
  eapply lb_trans; eauto.
  rewrite Hnblt.
  destruct (beq_dec a a') as [Hbeq | Hnbeq].
    rewrite Hbeq.
    simpl.
    split; trivial.
  rewrite Hnbeq.
  simpl.
  split.
    eapply lb_set'_gt; eauto.
    blt_simpl_tac.
  apply (IHrl' Hrl').
Qed.

Definition set (m : map) (a : A) (b : B) : map :=
  @listset_con (set' a b (lst m))
         (@is_orderset_set' (lst m) (prf m) a b).

Lemma set_sem_old : ∀ m a a' b,
  match (beq a a') with
    | true ⇒ get (set m a b) a = Some b
    | false ⇒ get (set m a b) a' = get m a'
  end.
Proof.
  intros m a a' b.
  unfold get, set.
  destruct m as [m prf0].
  destruct (beq_dec a a') as [Heq | Hneq].
    rewrite Heq.
    simpl.
    eapply get'_set'; eauto.
  rewrite Hneq.
  simpl.
  eapply get'_set'_neq; eauto.
  beq_simpl_tac.
Qed.

Lemma set_sem : ∀ m a a' b,
  get (set m a b) a' =
  match (beq a a') with
    | true ⇒ Some b
    | false ⇒ get m a'
  end.
  intros.
  assert (H := set_sem_old). substH H with (H m a a' b).
  assert (H1 := beq_true_eq). substH H1 with (H1 a a').
  assert (H2 := beq_false_neq). substH H2 with (H2 a a').
  destruct (beq a a').
  substH H1 with (H1 (refl_equal _)).
  rewrite H1 in H; rewrite H1; trivial.
  trivial.
Qed.

extensionality

Lemma equal_ext: ∀ m1 m2, (lst m1) = (lst m2) → m1 = m2.
Proof.
  destruct m1 as [m1 prf1].
  destruct m2 as [m2 prf2].
  simpl.
  intros.
  subst m1.
  rewrite (proof_irrelevance _ prf1 prf2).
  auto.
Qed.

Lemma extensionality: ∀ (m1 m2 : map),
  (∀ a, get m1 a = get m2 a) → m1 = m2.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 H.
  apply equal_ext.
  destruct m1 as [m1 prf1].
  destruct m2 as [m2 prf2].
  gen_clear m1 m2 prf1 prf2 H.
  induction m1 as [|(a1, b1) m1' IHm1'];
    unfold get, get', lst;
      cbv beta in *; fold get' in *;
        intros.

  induction m2 as [|(a2, b2) m2' IHm2'];
    unfold get, get', lst;
      cbv beta in *; fold get' in ×.
  reflexivity.
  simpl in H.
  assert (H2 := H a2).
    beq_simpl_tac.
    discriminate.
  destruct m2 as [|(a2,b2) m2']; simpl in × .
  assert (H1 := H a1).
    beq_simpl_tac.
    discriminate.
  assert (He :
    ∀ a : A, get' m1' a = get' m2' a).
  destruct (blt_beq_dec a1 a2) as [ [Hb | Hb ] | Hb].
  substH H with (H a1).
  blt_simpl_tac.
  beq_simpl_tac.
  assert (Hf := @in_notlb m2' a1 b1).
  rewrite <- H in Hf; clear H.
  assert (Hlb := @lb_trans m2' a1 a2 (proj1 prf2) Hb).
  destruct (Hf (refl_equal _) Hlb).
  intro a; substH H with (H a).
  assert (H0 := @beq_true_eq a1 a2 Hb).
  subst a1.
  destruct (eq_dec a a2) as [Heq | Hneq].
  subst a2.
  blt_simpl_tac; beq_simpl_tac.
  rewrite (@lb_notin m1' a (proj1 prf1)).
  rewrite (@lb_notin m2' a (proj1 prf2)).
  trivial.
  beq_simpl_tac.
  trivial.
  substH H with (H a2).
  beq_simpl_tac.
  blt_simpl_tac.
  assert (Hf := @in_notlb m1' a2 b2).
  rewrite <- H in Hf; clear H.
  assert (Hlb := @lb_trans m1' a2 a1 (proj1 prf1) Hb).
  destruct (Hf (refl_equal _) Hlb).
  substH IHm1' with
    (IHm1' m2' (proj2 prf1) (proj2 prf2) He).
  subst m2'.
  assert (H1 := H a1).
  assert (H2 := H a2).
  beq_simpl_tac.
  beq_case_tac a1 a2; beq_simpl_tac.
    rewrite (@beq_true_eq a1 a2 Hb).
    injection H1; intro; subst; trivial.
  rewrite (@lb_notin m1' a1 (proj1 prf1)) in H1.
  discriminate.
Qed.

Lemma get_set_same : ∀ m a b, get m a = Some b → set m a b = m.
Proof.
  intros.
  apply extensionality; intros.
  rewrite set_sem.
  destruct (beq_dec a a0) as [ Heq | Hneq ].
  rewrite Heq.
  apply beq_true_eq in Heq; subst; auto.
  rewrite Hneq.
  auto.
Qed.

Lemmas Tactics
indom lookup

Definition indom (m : map) (a : A) :=
  ∃ b : B, get m a = Some b.

Definition lookup (m : map) (a : A) (b : B) :=
  get m a = Some b.

sub meq compat

Definition sub (m1 m2 : map) :=
  ∀ (a : A) (b : B),
    lookup m1 a b → lookup m2 a b.

Definition meq (m1 m2 : map) :=
  sub m1 m2 ∧ sub m2 m1.

Definition compat (m1 m2 : map) : Prop :=
  ∀ a : A,
    match get m1 a, get m2 a with
      | Some b1, Some b2 ⇒ b1 = b2
      | _, _ ⇒ True
    end.

disj

  Definition disj (m1 m2 : map) : Prop :=
    ∀ a : A,
      match get m1 a, get m2 a with
        | Some b, None ⇒ True
        | None, Some b ⇒ True
        | None, None ⇒ True
        | _ , _ ⇒ False
      end.

merge

Fixpoint app' (rl1 rl2 : rlist) {struct rl1} : rlist :=
  match rl1 with
    | nil ⇒ rl2
    | (a,b) :: rl1' ⇒
      (set' a b (app' rl1' rl2))
  end.

Lemma is_set_app' : ∀ (rl1 rl2 : rlist),
  is_orderset rl1 → is_orderset rl2 → is_orderset (app' rl1 rl2).
Proof.
  intros rl1 rl2 Hrl1 Hrl2.
  induction rl1 as [|(a', b') rl1' IHrl1'].
  simpl; trivial.
  simpl in ×.
  apply is_orderset_set'.
  apply (IHrl1' (proj2 Hrl1)).
Qed.

Definition merge (m1 : map) (m2 : map) : map :=
  @listset_con (app' (lst m1) (lst m2))
    (@is_set_app' _ _ (prf m1) (prf m2)).

Lemma merge_sem : ∀ (m1 m2 : map) (a : A),
    get (merge m1 m2) a
    = match (get m1 a, get m2 a) with
        | (Some b1, Some b2) ⇒ Some b1
        | (Some b1, None) ⇒ Some b1
        | (None, Some b2) ⇒ Some b2
        | (None, None) ⇒ None
      end.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 a.
  unfold merge, get.
  destruct m1 as [rl1 prf1].
  destruct m2 as [rl2 prf2].
  simpl.
  induction rl1 as [|(a', b') rl1' IHrl1'].
  simpl.
  destruct (get' rl2 a); trivial.
  simpl in ×.
  destruct (eq_dec a a') as [Heq | Hneq].
    subst a'; simpl.
    rewrite (get'_set' (app' rl1' rl2) a b').
    beq_simpl_tac.
    destruct (get' rl2 a); trivial.
    assert (Hneq' : a' ≠ a).
      intro H; apply Hneq; auto.
  beq_simpl_tac.
  rewrite (@get'_set'_neq (app' rl1' rl2)
    a' a b' Hneq').
  apply IHrl1'.
  apply (proj2 prf1).
Qed.


Fixpoint minus' (rl1 rl2 : rlist) {struct rl1} : rlist :=
  match rl1 with
    | nil ⇒ nil
    | (a,b) :: rl1' ⇒
      match (get' rl2 a) with
        | Some b' ⇒ (minus' rl1' rl2)
        | None ⇒ set' a b (minus' rl1' rl2)
      end
  end.

Lemma is_orderset_minus' : ∀ (rl1 rl2 : rlist),
  is_orderset rl1 → is_orderset (minus' rl1 rl2).
Proof.
  intros rl1 rl2 Hrl1.
  induction rl1 as [|(a', b') rl1' IHrl1'].
  simpl; trivial.
  simpl in ×.
  destruct (get' rl2 a').
  apply (IHrl1' (proj2 Hrl1)).
  apply is_orderset_set'.
  apply (IHrl1' (proj2 Hrl1)).
Qed.

Definition minus (m : map) (m1 : map) : map :=
  @listset_con (minus' (lst m) (lst m1))
    (@is_orderset_minus' _ _ (prf m)).

Lemma lb_minus' : ∀ (rl1 rl2 : rlist) (a : A),
  lb a rl1 → lb a (minus' rl1 rl2).
Proof.
  intros rl1 rl2.
  induction rl1 as [|(a', b') rl1' IHrl1'].
    intros a H.
    simpl; trivial.
  simpl in ×.
  intros a [Heq Hlb].
  destruct (get' rl2 a').
  apply (IHrl1' _ Hlb).
  apply lb_set'_gt; trivial.
  apply IHrl1'; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma minus_sem : ∀ (m m1 : map) (a : A),
    get (minus m m1) a
    = match (get m a, get m1 a) with
        | (Some b, Some b1) ⇒ None
        | (Some b1, None) ⇒ Some b1
        | (None, Some b2) ⇒ None
        | (None, None) ⇒ None
      end.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 a.
  unfold minus, get.
  destruct m1 as [rl1 prf1].
  destruct m2 as [rl2 prf2].
  simpl.
  induction rl1 as [|(a', b') rl1' IHrl1'].
    simpl.
    destruct (get' rl2 a); trivial.
  simpl in ×.
  destruct (eq_dec a a') as [Heq | Hneq].
    subst a'; simpl.
    beq_simpl_tac.
    destruct (get' rl2 a); trivial.
      destruct prf1.
      apply lb_notin; trivial.
    apply lb_minus'; trivial.
    apply get'_set'; trivial.
  assert (Hneq' : a' ≠ a).
    intro H; apply Hneq; auto.
  beq_simpl_tac.
  destruct (get' rl2 a').
    apply IHrl1'.
    destruct prf1.
    trivial.
  rewrite (@get'_set'_neq (minus' rl1' rl2)
    a' a b' Hneq').
  apply IHrl1'.
  apply (proj2 prf1).
Qed.

join

Definition join (m1 m2 m: map) :=
  ∀ a : A,
    match get m1 a, get m2 a, get m a with
      | None, Some b1, Some b2 ⇒ b1 = b2
      | Some b1, None, Some b2 ⇒ b1 = b2
      | None, None, None ⇒ True
      | _, _, _ ⇒ False
    end.

Definition join3 (m1 m2 m3 m: map) :=
  ∀ a : A,
    match get m1 a, get m2 a, get m3 a, get m a with
      | Some b1, None, None, Some b2 ⇒ b1 = b2
      | None, Some b1, None, Some b2 ⇒ b1 = b2
      | None, None, Some b1, Some b2 ⇒ b1 = b2
      | None, None, None, None ⇒ True
      | _, _, _, _ ⇒ False
    end.

Lemmas Tactics
get set

Ltac destruct_get :=
  match goal with
  
    | H: context [ get ?m ?a ] |- _ ⇒
        destruct (get m a);
          destruct_get

    | |- context [ get ?m ?a ] ⇒
        destruct (get m a);
          destruct_get

    | _ ⇒ idtac

end.

Ltac rewrite_get :=
  match goal with

    | H: context [ get (merge ?m1 ?m2) ?a ] |- _ ⇒
        rewrite (merge_sem m1 m2 a) in H;
        rewrite_get

    | H: context [ get (set ?m ?a ?b) ?a' ] |- _ ⇒
        rewrite (set_sem m a a' b) in H;
        beq simpl;
        rewrite_get

    | H: context [ get (sig ?a ?b) ?a' ] |- _ ⇒
        rewrite (sig_sem a a' b) in H;
        beq simpl;
        rewrite_get

    | H: context [ get emp ?a ] |- _ ⇒
        rewrite (emp_sem a) in H;
        rewrite_get

    | |- context [ get (merge ?m1 ?m2) ?a ] ⇒
        rewrite (merge_sem m1 m2 a);
        rewrite_get

    | |- context [ get (set ?m ?a ?b) ?a' ] ⇒
        rewrite (set_sem m a a' b);
        beq simpl;
        rewrite_get

    | |- context [ get (sig ?a ?b) ?a' ] ⇒
        rewrite (sig_sem a a' b);
        beq simpl;
        rewrite_get

    | |- context [ get emp ?a ] ⇒
        rewrite (emp_sem a);
        rewrite_get

    | _ ⇒ idtac

end.

Ltac solve_sn :=
  match goal with

    | H: context [ Some ?x = Some ?y ] |-
         context [ ?x = ?y ] ⇒
        injection H;
        solve_sn

    | H: context [ Some ?y = Some ?x ] |-
         context [ ?x = ?y ] ⇒
        injection H;
        solve_sn

    | H: context [ Some ?x = None ] |- _⇒
        apply False_ind;
        discriminate;
        solve_sn

    | H: context [ None = Some ?x ] |- _ ⇒
        apply False_ind;
        discriminate;
        solve_sn

    | H: context [ ?x = ?y ] |-
         context [ Some ?x = Some ?z ] ⇒
        subst;
        solve_sn

    | H: context [ ?y = ?x ] |-
         context [ Some ?x = Some ?z ] ⇒
        subst;
        solve_sn

    | H: context [ _ → Some ?x = Some ?y] |-
         context [ Some ?x = Some ?y ] ⇒
        apply H;
        solve_sn

    | H: context [ _ → Some ?x = None ] |-
         context [ Some ?x = None ] ⇒
        apply H;
        solve_sn

    | H: context [ _ → None = Some ?x] |-
         context [ None = Some ?x] ⇒
        apply H;
        solve_sn

    | |- context [_ → _] ⇒
        intros;
        solve_sn

    | _ ⇒ try tauto || auto

end.

Lemma get_sig : ∀ (a a' : A) (b : B),
  get (sig a b) a' = match (eq_dec a a') with
                      | left _ ⇒ Some b
                       | right _ ⇒ None
                     end.
Proof.
  intros.
  rewrite_get; trivial.
  destruct (eq_dec a a').
  beq_case_tac a a'; beq_simpl_tac; trivial.
  subst a.
  beq_simpl_tac.
  beq_case_tac a a'; beq_simpl_tac; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma get_sig_some : ∀ (a : A) (b : B),
    get (sig a b) a = Some b.
Proof.
  intros.
  rewrite_get.
  trivial.
Qed.

Lemma get_sig_none : ∀ (a a' : A) (b : B),
  a ≠ a'
  → get (sig a b) a' = None.
Proof.
  intros.
  rewrite_get.
  beq_case_tac a a'; beq_simpl_tac; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma get_a_sig_a : ∀ (a a' : A) (b : B),
  beq a a' = true → get (sig a b) a' = Some b.
Proof.
  intros.
  rewrite_get.
  trivial.
Qed.

Lemma get_a_sig_a' : ∀ (a a' : A) (b : B),
  beq a a' = false → get (sig a b) a' = None.
Proof.
  intros.
  rewrite_get.
  trivial.
Qed.

Lemma get_sig_some_eq : ∀ (a a' : A) (b : B),
  get (sig a b) a' = Some b → a = a'.
Proof.
  intros.
  beq_case_tac a a'.
    beq_rewrite_tac Hb.
    trivial.
  rewrite get_a_sig_a' in H; trivial.
  discriminate H.
Qed.

Lemma get_sig_some_eq' : ∀ (a a' : A) (b b' : B),
  get (sig a b) a' = Some b' → a = a' ∧ b = b'.
Proof.
  intros.
  beq_case_tac a a'.
    assert (a = a').
      beq_rewrite_tac Hb; trivial.
    split; trivial.
    subst a'.
    rewrite get_sig_some in H.
    inversion H; trivial.
  rewrite get_a_sig_a' in H; trivial.
  discriminate H.
Qed.

Lemma set_a_get_a : ∀ (m : map) (a a' : A) (b : B),
  beq a a' = true → get (set m a b) a' = Some b.
Proof.
  intros.
  rewrite_get.
  trivial.
Qed.

Lemma set_a_get_a' : ∀ (m : map) (a a' : A) (b : B),
  beq a a' = false → get (set m a b) a' = get m a'.
Proof.
  intros.
  rewrite_get.
  trivial.
Qed.

Lemma set_sig : ∀ a b b',
  set (sig a b) a b' = sig a b'.
Proof.
  intros a b b'.
  apply extensionality.
  intro a0.
  beq_case_tac a a0.
    rewrite set_sem.
    rewrite Hb.
    rewrite sig_sem.
    rewrite Hb.
    trivial.
  rewrite set_sem.
  rewrite Hb.
  rewrite sig_sem.
  rewrite Hb.
  rewrite sig_sem.
  rewrite Hb.
  trivial.
Qed.

Lemma set_emp_sig : ∀ a b,
  set emp a b = sig a b.
Proof.
  intros.
  apply extensionality.
  intros.
  beq_case_tac a a0.
Qed.

lookup

Lemma lookup_emp : ∀ (a : A) (b : B),
  lookup emp a b → False.
Proof.
  intros a b; unfold lookup.
  intros H; rewrite_get.
  discriminate.
Qed.

Lemma lookup_get : ∀ (m : map) (a : A) (b : B),
  lookup m a b
  → get m a = Some b.
Proof.
  intros m a b. unfold lookup. trivial.
Qed.

Lemma get_lookup : ∀ (m : map) (a : A) (b : B),
  get m a = Some b
    → lookup m a b.
Proof.
  intros; unfold lookup; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma lookup_unique : ∀ (m : map) (a : A) (b b' :B),
  lookup m a b → lookup m a b' → b = b'.
Proof.
  intros m a b b'; unfold lookup.
  intros H1 H2; rewrite H1 in H2; injection H2.
  trivial.
Qed.

indom <--> lookup

Lemma lookup_indom : ∀ (m : map) (a : A) (b : B),
    lookup m a b → indom m a.
Proof.
  intros m a b; unfold lookup, indom.
  intros H; ∃ b; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma indom_lookup : ∀ (m : map) (a : A),
  indom m a
  → ∃ b : B,
    lookup m a b.
Proof.
  intros m a; unfold indom, lookup; trivial.
Qed.

indom <---> get

Lemma indom_get : ∀ (m : map) (a : A),
  indom m a
  → ∃ b : B,
    get m a = Some b.
Proof.
  intros m a; unfold indom; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma get_indom : ∀ (m : map) (a : A),
  (∃ b : B, get m a = Some b)
  → indom m a.
Proof.
  intros m a; unfold indom; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma nindom_get :
  ∀ (m : map) (a : A),
    ¬ indom m a → get m a = None.
Proof.
  intros m a; unfold indom, not; trivial.
  destruct (get m a).
  intros H; elimtype False; apply H; ∃ b; trivial.
  trivial.
Qed.

sub meq compat

Lemma sub_refl : ∀ (m : map),
  sub m m.
Proof.
  intros m a; destruct (get m a); trivial.
Qed.

Implicit Arguments sub_refl[].

Lemma sub_asym : ∀ (m1 m2 : map),
  sub m1 m2
  → sub m2 m1
  → meq m1 m2.
Proof.
  unfold meq.
  auto.
Qed.

Lemma sub_trans : ∀ (m1 m2 m3 : map),
  sub m1 m2
  → sub m2 m3
  → sub m1 m3.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 m3; unfold sub.
  intros H1 H2 a b.
    substH H1 with (H1 a b);
    substH H2 with (H2 a b);
    auto.
Qed.
Implicit Arguments sub_trans[m1 m2 m3].

Lemma sub_sig : ∀ m a b,
  get m a = Some b
  → sub (sig a b) m.
Proof.
  unfold sub, lookup.
  intros.
  rewrite_get.
  beq_case_tac a a0.
    beq_simpl_tac.
    inversion H0.
    subst b0.
    beq_rewrite_tac Hb.
    trivial.
  beq_simpl_tac.
  discriminate.
Qed.

Lemma meq_refl : ∀ (m : map),
  meq m m.
Proof.
  intros m; unfold meq; split; apply sub_refl.
Qed.

Lemma meq_sym : ∀ (m1 m2 : map),
  meq m1 m2 → meq m2 m1.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2; unfold meq.
  intros [H1 H2]; split; assumption.
Qed.

Lemma meq_trans : ∀ (m1 m2 m3 : map),
  meq m1 m2
  → meq m2 m3
  → meq m1 m3.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 m3; unfold meq, sub.
  intros [H1 H2] [H3 H4];
    split; intros a b;
    substH H1 with (H1 a b);
    substH H2 with (H2 a b);
    substH H3 with (H3 a b);
    substH H4 with (H4 a b);
    tauto.
Qed.

Lemma meq_sem : ∀ (m1 m2 : map),
  meq m1 m2 →
  ∀ (a : A),
    match get m1 a, get m2 a with
      | Some b1, Some b2 ⇒ b1 = b2
      | None, None ⇒ True
      | _, _ ⇒ False
    end.
Proof.
  unfold meq, sub, lookup.
  intros m1 m2 [H1 H2] a.
  substH H1 with (H1 a).
  substH H2 with (H2 a).
  destruct_get; auto.
  substH H2 with (H2 b (refl_equal _)).
  injection H2.
  trivial.
  substH H2 with (H2 b (refl_equal _)).
  discriminate.
  substH H1 with (H1 b (refl_equal _)).
  discriminate.
Qed.

Lemma meq_eq : ∀ m1 m2 : map,
  meq m1 m2 → m1 = m2.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 H.
  assert (H' := @meq_sem m1 m2 H).
  apply extensionality.
  intro a.
  substH H' with (H' a).
  destruct (get m1 a); destruct (get m2 a); simpl; subst; trivial.
  destruct H'.
  destruct H'.
Qed.

Lemma compat_refl : ∀ m : map,
  compat m m.
Proof.
  unfold compat.
  intros.
  destruct_get; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma compat_sym : ∀ (m1 m2 : map),
  compat m1 m2 → compat m2 m1.
Proof.
  unfold compat; intros m1 m2 H a.
  substH H with (H a).
  destruct_get;
    auto.
Qed.

get <--> sub lookup <--> sub

Lemma get_sub_get : ∀ (m1 m2 : map) (a : A) (b : B),
  get m1 a = Some b → sub m1 m2 → get m2 a = Some b.
Proof.
  unfold sub.
  intros m1 m2 a b H H1.
  substH H1 with (H1 a b).
  apply (H1 H).
Qed.

Lemma lookup_sub_lookup : ∀ (m1 m2 : map) (a : A) (b : B),
  lookup m1 a b → sub m1 m2 → lookup m2 a b.
Proof.
  unfold sub.
  intros m1 m2 a b H H1.
  substH H1 with (H1 a b).
  apply (H1 H).
Qed.

Lemma indom_sub_indom : ∀ m1 m2 a,
    indom m1 a → sub m1 m2 → indom m2 a.
Proof.
  unfold meq, sub.
  intros m1 m2 a H H1.
  substH H with (indom_lookup H).
  destruct H as [b H].
  substH H1 with (H1 a b).
  apply (lookup_indom (H1 H)).
Qed.

lookup <--> meq

Lemma lookup_meq_lookup : ∀ (m1 m2 : map) (a : A) (b : B),
  lookup m1 a b → meq m1 m2 → lookup m2 a b.
Proof.
  unfold meq, sub.
  intros m1 m2 a b H0 [H1 H2].
  substH H1 with (H1 a b);
  substH H2 with (H2 a b).
  apply (H1 H0).
Qed.

Lemma indom_meq_indom : ∀ m1 m2 a,
    indom m1 a → meq m1 m2 → indom m2 a.
Proof.
  unfold meq, sub.
  intros m1 m2 a H [H1 H2].
  substH H with (indom_lookup H).
  destruct H as [b H].
  substH H1 with (H1 a b);
  substH H2 with (H2 a b).
  apply (lookup_indom (H1 H)).
Qed.

  disj m1 m2
  → disj m2 m1.

Lemma disj_sig : ∀ (a a' : A) (b b' : B),
  beq a a' = false
  → disj (sig a b) (sig a' b').
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold disj.
  intros a0.
  beq_case_tac a a0; beq_case_tac a' a0.
  destruct_get; trivial.
  beq_rewriteH_tac Hb H.
  beq_rewriteH_tac Hb0 H.
  beq_simpl_tac.
  rewrite (@get_a_sig_a' a' a0); trivial.
  destruct_get; trivial.
  rewrite (@get_a_sig_a' a a0); trivial.
  destruct_get; trivial.
  rewrite (@get_a_sig_a' a a0); trivial.
  rewrite (@get_a_sig_a' a' a0); trivial.
Qed.

indom <---> disj

Lemma disj_indom :
  ∀ (m1 m2 : map),
    disj m1 m2
    → (∀ a : A,
      (indom m1 a → ¬ indom m2 a)
      ∧ (indom m2 a → ¬ indom m1 a)).
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 H a; unfold indom, not;
    substH H with (H a);split;
      intros H1 H2;
        destruct H1 as [b1 H1];
          destruct H2 as [b2 H2];
            destruct_get; solve_sn.
Qed.

Lemma indom_disj : ∀ (m1 m2 : map),
  (∀ a : A,
    (indom m1 a → ¬ indom m2 a)
    ∧ (indom m2 a → ¬ indom m1 a))
  → disj m1 m2.
Proof.
  unfold indom, disj, not.
  intros m1 m2 H a.
    substH H with (H a).
  destruct H as [H1 H2].
    destruct_get; solve_sn.
  apply H1.
  ∃ b0; trivial.
  ∃ b; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma disj_meq_disj_r : ∀ (m1 m2 m3 : map),

Qed.

Lemma meq_merge_meq :
  ∀ m1 m2 m3 m4,
    meq m1 m3 → meq m2 m4
    → meq (merge m1 m2) (merge m3 m4).
Proof.
  unfold meq, sub, lookup.
  intros m1 m2 m3 m4 [H1 H2] [H3 H4].
  split; intros a b;
    substH H1 with (H1 a);
    substH H2 with (H2 a);
    substH H3 with (H3 a);
    substH H4 with (H4 a);
  rewrite_get;
  intros H;
    destruct (get m1 a) as [b1 |];
    destruct (get m2 a) as [b2 |];
    destruct (get m3 a) as [b3 |];
    destruct (get m4 a) as [b4 |];
      auto.
  assert (Hf := H1 b H); discriminate.
  assert (Hf := H2 b3 (refl_equal _)); discriminate.
  assert (Hf := H1 b1 (refl_equal _)); discriminate.
  assert (Hf := H2 b H); discriminate.
Qed.

Lemma lookup_merge_elim :

    lookup (merge m1 m2) a b
    → lookup m1 a b ∨ lookup m2 a b.

Qed.

Lemma lookup_merge_intro :
  ∀ (m1 m2 : map) (a : A) (b : B),
    lookup m1 a b ∨ lookup m2 a b
    → compat m1 m2
    → lookup (merge m1 m2) a b.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 a b.
  unfold lookup, compat; rewrite_get.
  intros [H1 | H2]; intros H;
    substH H with (H a);
    destruct_get;
      solve_sn.
Qed.

Lemma indom_merge_intro :
  ∀ (m1 m2 : map) (a : A),
    indom m1 a ∨ indom m2 a
    → indom (merge m1 m2) a.
Proof.
  unfold indom.
  intros m1 m2 a [[b H]|[b H]];
  rewrite_get;
    destruct_get; solve_sn.
  ∃ b0; trivial.
  ∃ b0; trivial.
  ∃ b1; trivial.
  ∃ b; trivial.
Qed.

  ∀ (m1 m2 : map) (a : A),
  indom (merge m1 m2) a
  → indom m1 a ∨ indom m2 a.

  unfold indom.
  intros m1 m2 a [b H].
  rewrite_get;
    destruct_get; solve_sn.
  left; ∃ b; assumption.
  left; ∃ b; assumption.
  right; ∃ b; assumption.
Qed.

Lemma disj_merge_intro_l :

    disj m1 m3 ∧ disj m2 m3
    → disj (merge m1 m2) m3.
Proof.
  unfold disj.
  intros m1 m2 m3 [H1 H2] a.
  substH H1 with (H1 a).
  substH H2 with (H2 a).
  rewrite_get;
    destruct_get; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma disj_merge_elim_l :
  ∀ (m1 m2 m3 : map),
    disj (merge m1 m2) m3
    → disj m1 m3 ∧ disj m2 m3.
Proof.
  unfold disj.
  intros m1 m2 m3 H.
  split; intro a; substH H with (H a);
    rewrite_get;
      destruct_get; solve_sn.
Qed.

Lemma disj_merge_intro_r :
  ∀ (m1 m2 m3 : map),
    disj m1 m2 ∧ disj m1 m3
    → disj m1 (merge m2 m3).

  intros.

  elim H; intros; split; apply disj_sym; trivial.

Lemma disj_merge_elim_r :
  ∀ (m1 m2 m3 : map),
    disj m1 (merge m2 m3)

  elim H; split; intros;
  apply disj_sym; assumption.
Qed.

Lemma disj_merge_intro_lr :
  ∀ (m1 m2 m1' m2' : map),
    disj m1 m1'
    → disj m1 m2'
    → disj m2 m1'
    → disj m2 m2'
    → disj (merge m1 m2) (merge m1' m2').

  intros m1 m2 m1' m2' H1 H2 H3 H4 a.
  substH H1 with (H1 a);
  substH H2 with (H2 a);
  substH H3 with (H3 a);
  substH H4 with (H4 a).
  rewrite_get;
    destruct_get; solve_sn.
Qed.

Lemma disj_merge_elim_lr :
  ∀ (m1 m2 m1' m2' : map),
    disj (merge m1' m2') (merge m1 m2)
    → (disj m1 m1' ∧ disj m1 m2')
    ∧ (disj m2 m1' ∧ disj m2 m2').
Proof.
  unfold disj.
  intros m1 m2 m1' m2' H.
  split; split; intro a;
  substH H with (H a);
  rewrite_get;
    destruct_get; solve_sn.
Qed.

join lemmas


Lemma join_comm :
  ∀ ma mb mab : map,
    join ma mb mab → join mb ma mab.
Proof.
  intros ma mb mab.
  unfold join.
  intros H a.
  substH H with (H a).
  destruct_get; auto.
Qed.

Lemma join_assoc_l :
  ∀ ma mb mc mab mabc,
    join ma mb mab→
    join mab mc mabc →
    ∃ mbc, join mb mc mbc ∧
      join ma mbc mabc.
Proof.
  intros ma mb mc mab mabc.
  unfold join.
  intros H1 H2.
  ∃ (merge mb mc).
  split; intros a;
    rewrite_get;
    substH H1 with (H1 a);
    substH H2 with (H2 a);
    destruct_get; solve_sn.
  rewrite H1; trivial.
  rewrite H1; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma join_assoc_r :
  ∀ ma mb mc mbc mabc,
    join mb mc mbc→
    join ma mbc mabc →
    ∃ mab, join ma mb mab ∧
      join mab mc mabc.
Proof.
  intros ma mb mc mbc mabc.
  unfold join.
  intros H1 H2.
  ∃ (merge ma mb).
  split; intros a;
    rewrite_get;
    substH H1 with (H1 a);
    substH H2 with (H2 a);
    destruct_get; solve_sn.
  rewrite H1; trivial.
  rewrite H1; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma join_disj_meq :
  ∀ (m1 m2 m : map),
    join m1 m2 m
    → disj m1 m2 ∧ meq (merge m1 m2) m.
Proof.
  unfold join, disj, meq,sub, lookup.
  split; intros; try split; intros; substH H with (H a);
  rewrite_get;
    destruct_get; solve_sn.
Qed.

Lemma disj_meq_join :
  ∀ (m1 m2 m: map),
    disj m1 m2 ∧ meq (merge m1 m2) m
    → join m1 m2 m.
Proof.
  unfold disj, meq,sub, lookup.
  intros m1 m2 m [H0 [H1 H2]] a.
  substH H0 with (H0 a);
  substH H1 with (H1 a);
  substH H2 with (H2 a).
  rewrite_get;
  destruct_get;
    (try substH H2
      with (H2 b (refl_equal _));
      (injection H2 || discriminate || trivial;
        trivial))
|| (try substH H2
      with (H1 b (refl_equal _));
      (injection H1 || discriminate || trivial;
        trivial));
    trivial.
Qed.

Lemma join_sub_l :
  ∀ m1 m2 m,
    join m1 m2 m
    → sub m1 m.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 m.
  unfold join, sub, lookup; intros H.
  intro a.
  substH H with (H a).
  destruct_get;
    solve_sn.
Qed.

Lemma join_sub_r :
  ∀ m1 m2 m,
    join m1 m2 m
    → sub m2 m.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 m.
  unfold join, sub, lookup; intros H.
  intro a.
  substH H with (H a).
  destruct_get; solve_sn.
Qed.
Implicit Arguments join_sub_r [m1 m2 m].

Lemma join_unique :
  ∀ m1 m2 m m',
  join m1 m2 m →
  join m1 m2 m' →
  m = m'.
Proof.
  intros.
  apply join_disj_meq in H.
  apply join_disj_meq in H0.
  destruct H.
  destruct H0.
  apply meq_eq in H1.
  apply meq_eq in H2.
  rewrite H1 in H2.
  assumption.
Qed.

Lemma join_lookup_lookup_l :
  ∀ m1 m2 m a b,
    join m1 m2 m
    → lookup m1 a b
    → lookup m a b.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 m a b Hj H1.
  assert (H:= join_sub_l Hj).
  unfold sub in H.
  apply (H a b H1).
Qed.

Lemma join_lookup_lookup_r :
  ∀ m1 m2 m a b,
    join m1 m2 m
    → lookup m2 a b
    → lookup m a b.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 m a b Hj H2.
  assert (H:= join_sub_r Hj).
  unfold sub in H.

Qed.

Lemma join_get_get_l :
  ∀ m1 m2 m a b,
    join m1 m2 m
    → get m1 a = Some b
    → get m a = Some b.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 m a b Hj H1.

  unfold sub, lookup in H.
  apply (H a b H1).
Qed.

Lemma join_get_get_r :
  ∀ m1 m2 m a b,
    join m1 m2 m
    → get m2 a = Some b
    → get m a = Some b.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 m a b Hj H2.

Qed.

Lemma join_merge_disj :
  ∀ m1 m2,
    disj m1 m2 →
    join m1 m2 (merge m1 m2).
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold disj in ×.
  unfold join.
  intros.
  assert (match get m1 a with
      | Some _ ⇒ match get m2 a with
                  | Some _ ⇒ False
                  | None ⇒ True
                  end
      | None ⇒ match get m2 a with
                | Some _ ⇒ True
                | None ⇒ True
                end
      end).
  apply H.
  clear H.
  rewrite merge_sem.
  destruct (get m1 a);destruct (get m2 a);trivial;assumption.
Qed.

Lemma join_lookup_or :
  ∀ m1 m2 m a b,
    join m1 m2 m →
    lookup m a b →
    (lookup m1 a b) ∨ (lookup m2 a b).
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold lookup in ×.
  unfold join in H.
  assert (match get m1 a with
      | Some b1 ⇒
          match get m2 a with
          | Some _ ⇒ False
          | None ⇒
              match get m a with
              | Some b2 ⇒ b1 = b2
              | None ⇒ False
              end
          end
      | None ⇒
          match get m2 a with
          | Some b1 ⇒
              match get m a with
              | Some b2 ⇒ b1 = b2
              | None ⇒ False
              end
          | None ⇒ match get m a with
                    | Some _ ⇒ False
                    | None ⇒ True
                    end
          end
      end).
  apply H.
  clear H.
  rewrite H0 in H1.
  destruct (get m1 a);destruct (get m2 a);destruct H1;try (left;reflexivity);try (right;reflexivity).
Qed.

Lemma join_get_or :
  ∀ m1 m2 m a b,
    join m1 m2 m →
    get m a = Some b →
    (get m1 a = Some b) ∨ (get m2 a = Some b).
Proof.
  intros.
  apply get_lookup in H0.
  destruct (join_lookup_or H H0).
  left; apply get_lookup; trivial.
  right; apply get_lookup; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma join_set_l :
  ∀ m1 m2 m a b,
    join m1 m2 m
    → indom m1 a
    → join (set m1 a b) m2 (set m a b).
Proof.
  unfold indom, join.
  intros m1 m2 m a b H H1.
  intro a0.
  substH H with (H a0).
  destruct H1.
  rewrite_get.
  beq_case_tac a a0; beq simpl; trivial.
  assert (a = a0).
    beq rewrite Hb; trivial.
  subst a0.
  rewrite_get;

  trivial.
Qed.

Ltac find_join_eql :=
  match goal with
    | H: join ?ma _ _ |-
         join ?ma ?mb ?mab ⇒
        eapply H

    | H: join _ ?ma _ |-
         join ?ma ?mb ?mab ⇒
        apply join_comm; eapply H

    | H: join ?mb _ _ |-
         join ?ma ?mb ?mab ⇒
        apply join_comm; eapply H

    | H: join _ ?mb _ |-
         join ?ma ?mb ?mab ⇒
        eapply H
    
    | H: join _ _ ?mab |-
         join ?ma ?mb ?mab ⇒
        eapply H
  end.

Ltac solve_get :=
  match goal with
    | H: get ?m ?x = _ |-
         get ?m ?x = _ ⇒
       eapply H
    | H: join (sig ?x _) _ ?m |-
         get ?m ?x = Some _ ⇒
        eapply join_sig_get;
        eapply H
    | |- get (sig ?x _) ?x = Some _ ⇒
        eapply get_sig_some
    | H: join ?ma ?mb ?mab |-
         get ?mab ?x = Some ?v ⇒
         match goal with
           | H': get ?ma ?x = Some ?v |- _ ⇒
               eapply join_get_l; [eapply H | eapply H']
           | H': get ?mb ?x = Some ?v |- _ ⇒
               eapply join_get_r; [eapply H | eapply H']
         end
  end.

Ltac solve_sub :=
  match goal with
    | H: join ?ma ?mb ?mab |-
         sub ?ma ?mab ⇒
        eapply join_sub_l; eapply H
    | H: join ?ma ?mb ?mab |-
         sub ?mb ?mab ⇒
        eapply join_sub_r; eapply H
  end.

Ltac solve_disj :=
  match goal with
    | H: disj ?ma ?mb |-
         disj ?ma ?mb ⇒
        apply H
    | H: disj ?ma ?mb |-
         disj ?mb ?ma ⇒
        apply disj_sym; apply H
    | H: join ?ma ?mb ?mab |-
         disj ?ma ?mb ⇒
        eapply my_join_disj; eapply H
    | H: join ?ma ?mb ?mab |-
         disj ?mb ?ma ⇒
        eapply disj_sym; eapply my_join_disj; eapply H
  end.

Ltac solve_join :=
  match goal with
    | H: join _ _ ?mab |-
         join _ _ ?mab ⇒
        first [eapply H | apply join_comm; eapply H | idtac]
  end.

Ltac solve_map :=
  match goal with
    | |- get _ _ = _ ⇒
        try solve_get
    | |- sub _ _ ⇒
        try solve_sub
    | |- disj _ _ ⇒
        try solve_disj
    | |- join _ _ _ ⇒
        try solve_join
    | _ ⇒ idtac
  end.

Fixpoint mapmap' (lst: rlist) (f: B→B) :rlist :=
  match lst with
    | nil ⇒ nil
    | (i,ac)::lst' ⇒ (i, f ac):: (mapmap' lst' f)
  end.

Lemma lb_mapmap':

    is_orderset lst →

Definition mapmap (m: map) (f: B→B) :map :=
  @listset_con (mapmap' (lst m) f) (is_orderset_mapmap' f (prf m)).

Lemma mapmap_sem : ∀ (m: map) (f : B→B) (a: A),
    get (mapmap m f) a
    = match (get m a) with
        | Some b ⇒ Some (f b)
        | None ⇒ None
      end.
Proof.
  intros m f a.
  unfold mapmap, get.
  destruct m as [rl prf].
  simpl.
  induction rl as [| (a',b') rl' IHrl'].

  simpl; auto.

  simpl.
  destruct prf as [Hlb prf].
  destruct (eq_dec a' a) as [Heq | Hneq].
  subst a'; simpl.
  beq_simpl_tac; auto.
  beq_simpl_tac.
  eauto.
Qed.

Proof.
  intros.
  unfold eqdom.
  unfold indom.
  intros.
  rewrite mapmap_sem.
  destruct (get m x).

  split; eauto.

  split; congruence.
Qed.

Lemma disj_mapmap_disj:
  ∀ m m' f
         (Hdisj: disj m' m),
    disj (mapmap m' f) m.
Proof.
  intros.
  apply disj_eqdom_disj with (m1:=m'); eauto.
  apply mapmap_eqdom; auto.
Qed.

Lemma mapmap_merge_eq:
  ∀ m1 m2 f,
    mapmap (merge m1 m2) f = merge (mapmap m1 f) (mapmap m2 f).
Proof.
  intros.
  apply extensionality.
  intros.
  rewrite mapmap_sem.
  rewrite merge_sem.
  rewrite merge_sem.
  rewrite mapmap_sem.
  rewrite mapmap_sem.
  destruct (get m1 a); destruct (get m2 a); auto.
Qed.

Lemma merge_get:
  ∀ m1 m2 a b
         (Hget: get (merge m1 m2) a = Some b),
   get m1 a = Some b ∨ (get m1 a = None ∧ get m2 a = Some b).
Proof.
  intros.
  rewrite merge_sem in Hget.
  destruct (get m1 a); destruct (get m2 a); try congruence; auto.
Qed.

Lemma merge_get_l:
  ∀ m1 m2 a b
         (Hget: get m1 a = Some b),
    get (merge m1 m2) a = Some b.
Proof.
  intros.
  rewrite merge_sem.
  rewrite Hget.
  destruct (get m2 a); auto.
Qed.

Lemma merge_get_r:
  ∀ m1 m2 a b
         (Hget1: get m1 a = None)
         (Hget2: get m2 a = Some b),
    get (merge m1 m2) a = Some b.
Proof.
  intros.
  rewrite merge_sem.
  rewrite Hget1.
  rewrite Hget2.
  auto.
Qed.

Lemma join_merge:
  ∀ m1 m2 m
         (Hjoin: join m1 m2 m),
    m = merge m1 m2.
Proof.
  intros.
  apply extensionality.
  intros.
  specialize (Hjoin a).
  unfold join in Hjoin.
  rewrite merge_sem.
  destruct (get m1 a); destruct (get m2 a); destruct (get m a);
  (try solve [exfalso; auto]);
  (try solve [congruence]).
Qed.

Lemma eqdom_join_partition:
  ∀ m1 m2 m m'
         (Heqdom: eqdom m m')
         (Hjoin: join m1 m2 m),
  ∃ m1' m2', join m1' m2' m' ∧ eqdom m1 m1' ∧ eqdom m2 m2'.
Proof.
  intros.
  ∃ (minus m' m2), (minus m' m1).
  split.

  unfold join in ×.
  unfold eqdom in ×.
  unfold indom in ×.
  intros.
  specialize (Hjoin a).
  specialize (Heqdom a).
  repeat rewrite minus_sem.
  destruct (get m1 a); destruct (get m2 a); destruct (get m a); destruct (get m' a); auto.
  destruct Heqdom as [Heqdom1 Heqdom2].
  assert (∃ b': B, None = Some b') as Hfalse
      by eauto.
  destruct Hfalse as [b' Hfalse].
  congruence.

  split.
  unfold eqdom in ×.
  unfold indom in ×.
  unfold join in ×.
  intros.
  specialize (Heqdom x).
  specialize (Hjoin x).
  split.
eqdom ->
  intros Hget.
  destruct Hget as [b Hget].
  rewrite minus_sem.
  destruct (get m1 x); destruct (get m2 x); destruct (get m x); destruct (get m' x);
    (try solve [exfalso; auto]);
    (try solve [congruence]);
    (try solve [eauto]).

  assert (∃ b: B, None = Some b)
    by (apply Heqdom; eauto).
  congruence.

eqdom <-
  intros Hget.
  destruct Hget as [b Hget].
  rewrite minus_sem in ×.
  destruct (get m1 x); destruct (get m2 x); destruct (get m x); destruct (get m' x);
    (try solve [exfalso; auto]);
    (try solve [congruence]);
    (try solve [eauto]).

  assert (∃ b: B, None = Some b)
    by (apply Heqdom; eauto).
  congruence.

  unfold eqdom in ×.
  unfold indom in ×.
  unfold join in ×.
  intros.
  specialize (Heqdom x).
  specialize (Hjoin x).
  split.
eqdom ->
  intros Hget.
  destruct Hget as [b Hget].
  rewrite minus_sem.
  destruct (get m1 x); destruct (get m2 x); destruct (get m x); destruct (get m' x);
    (try solve [exfalso; auto]);
    (try solve [congruence]);
    (try solve [eauto]).

  assert (∃ b: B, None = Some b)
    by (apply Heqdom; eauto).
  congruence.

eqdom <-
  intros Hget.
  destruct Hget as [b Hget].
  rewrite minus_sem in ×.
  destruct (get m1 x); destruct (get m2 x); destruct (get m x); destruct (get m' x);
    (try solve [exfalso; auto]);
    (try solve [congruence]);
    (try solve [eauto]).

  assert (∃ b: B, None = Some b)
    by (apply Heqdom; eauto).
  congruence.
Qed.

Lemma con_join:
  ∀ a b lst0
         (lbprf: lb a lst0)
         (prf: is_orderset lst0),
    join (sig a b) (listset_con (lst:=lst0) prf) (listset_con (lst:=(a,b)::lst0) (conj lbprf prf)).
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold join.
  unfold sig.
  unfold get; simpl.
  intros.
  remember (beq a0 a) as v.
  apply eq_sym in Heqv.
  destruct v.
  apply beq_true_eq in Heqv.
  subst.
  rewrite lb_notin; auto.
  destruct (get' lst0 a0); auto.
Qed.

Lemma sig_eqdom_sig:
  ∀ a b m
         (Heqdom: eqdom (sig a b) m),
    ∃ b', m = sig a b'.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold eqdom in Heqdom.
  pose (Heqdom a) as Heqdom_aux.
  unfold indom in Heqdom_aux.
  rewrite get_sig in Heqdom_aux.
  destruct (eq_dec a a); try congruence.
  assert (∃ b:B, get m a = Some b) as Hget
      by (apply Heqdom_aux; eauto).
  destruct Hget as [b' Hget].
  ∃ b'.
  apply extensionality.
  intros.
  destruct (eq_dec a a0).
  subst.
  rewrite get_sig.
  destruct (eq_dec a0 a0); try congruence.
  specialize (Heqdom a0).
  unfold indom in Heqdom.
  rewrite get_sig_none; auto.
  destruct (get m a0); auto.
  assert (∃ b1:B, get (sig a b) a0 = Some b1) as Hget'
      by (apply Heqdom; eauto).
  destruct Hget' as [b1 Hget'].
  rewrite get_sig_none in Hget'; auto.
  congruence.
Qed.

Lemma set_sig_mapmap:
  ∀ a b f,
    set (sig a b) a (f b) = mapmap (sig a b) f.
Proof.
  intros.
  apply extensionality.
  intros.
  destruct (eq_dec a a0).
  subst.
  rewrite set_a_get_a; try (rewrite eq_beq_true;auto).
  rewrite mapmap_sem.
  rewrite get_sig_some; auto.
  rewrite set_a_get_a'; try (rewrite neq_beq_false;auto).
  rewrite mapmap_sem.
  rewrite get_sig_none; auto.
Qed.

Lemma eqdom_set_set:
  ∀ m1 m2 a b1 b2
         (Heqdom: eqdom m1 m2),
    eqdom (set m1 a b1) (set m2 a b2).
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold eqdom in ×.
  intros.
  unfold indom in ×.
  destruct (eq_dec a x).

  subst x.
  rewrite set_a_get_a; try (rewrite eq_beq_true; auto).
  rewrite set_a_get_a; try (rewrite eq_beq_true; auto).
  split; eauto.

  rewrite set_a_get_a'; try (rewrite neq_beq_false; auto).
  rewrite set_a_get_a'; try (rewrite neq_beq_false; auto).
  eauto.
Qed.

End MapFun.

Module MAP_DOMAIN_EQ (A: MAP_DOMAIN) (B1 B2: MAP_RANGE).
 Module M1:= MapFun A B1.
 Module M2:= MapFun A B2.
 Definition eqdom (m1: M1.map) (m2: M2.map) :=
   ∀ x, M1.indom m1 x ↔ M2.indom m2 x.

 Definition disj (m1: M1.map) (m2 : M2.map) : Prop :=
    ∀ a,
      match M1.get m1 a, M2.get m2 a with
        | Some b, None ⇒ True
        | None, Some b ⇒ True
        | None, None ⇒ True
        | _ , _ ⇒ False
      end.

Lemma sig_eqdom_sig:
  ∀ a b m
         (Heqdom: eqdom (M1.sig a b) m),
    ∃ b', m = M2.sig a b'.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold eqdom in Heqdom.
  pose (Heqdom a) as Heqdom_aux.
  unfold M1.indom in Heqdom_aux.
  rewrite M1.get_sig in Heqdom_aux.
  destruct (M1.eq_dec a a); try congruence.
  assert (∃ b:B2.B, M2.get m a = Some b) as Hget
      by (apply Heqdom_aux; eauto).
  destruct Hget as [b' Hget].
  ∃ b'.
  apply M2.extensionality.
  intros.
  destruct (M2.eq_dec a a0).
  subst.
  rewrite M2.get_sig.
  destruct (M2.eq_dec a0 a0); try congruence.
  specialize (Heqdom a0).
  unfold M2.indom in Heqdom.
  unfold M1.indom in Heqdom.
  rewrite M2.get_sig_none; auto.
  destruct (M2.get m a0); auto.
  assert (∃ b1:B1.B, M1.get (M1.sig a b) a0 = Some b1) as Hget'
      by (apply Heqdom; eauto).
  destruct Hget' as [b1 Hget'].
  rewrite M1.get_sig_none in Hget'; auto.
  congruence.
Qed.

Lemma sig_eqdom:
  ∀ a b1 b2,
    eqdom (M1.sig a b1) (M2.sig a b2).
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold eqdom.
  intros.
  unfold M1.indom; unfold M2.indom.
  split.
  intros Hget.
  destruct Hget as [b Hget].
  destruct (M1.eq_dec a x).
a = x
  subst.
  rewrite M2.get_sig_some; eauto.
a <> x
  rewrite M1.get_sig_none in Hget; auto.
  congruence.
  intros Hget.
  destruct Hget as [b Hget].
  destruct (M2.eq_dec a x).
a = x
  subst.
  rewrite M1.get_sig_some; eauto.
a <> x
  rewrite M2.get_sig_none in Hget; auto.
  congruence.
Qed.

Lemma eqdom_set_set:
  ∀ m1 m2 a b1 b2
         (Heqdom: eqdom m1 m2),
    eqdom (M1.set m1 a b1) (M2.set m2 a b2).
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold eqdom in ×.
  intros.
  unfold M1.indom in ×.
  unfold M2.indom in ×.
  destruct (M1.eq_dec a x).

  subst x.
  rewrite M1.set_a_get_a; try (rewrite A.eq_beq_true; auto).
  rewrite M2.set_a_get_a; try (rewrite A.eq_beq_true; auto).
  split; eauto.

  rewrite M1.set_a_get_a'; try (rewrite A.neq_beq_false; auto).
  rewrite M2.set_a_get_a'; try (rewrite A.neq_beq_false; auto).
  eauto.
Qed.

Lemma eqdom_emp_emp_l:
  ∀ (m: M1.map) (Heqdom: eqdom m M2.emp), m = M1.emp.
Proof.
  intros.
  apply M1.extensionality.
  intros.
  destruct m.
  induction lst.


  unfold M1.get.
  simpl.
  auto.

  destruct a0.
  unfold eqdom in Heqdom.
  specialize (Heqdom a0).
  destruct Heqdom as [Heqdom1 Heqdom2].
  assert (M1.indom (M1.listset_con (lst:=(a0, b) :: lst) i) a0)
    by (
        unfold M1.indom;
        ∃ b;
               unfold M1.get; simpl;
               rewrite A.eq_beq_true; auto).
  assert (M2.indom M2.emp a0) as Hfalse by auto.
  unfold M2.indom in Hfalse.
  rewrite M2.emp_sem in Hfalse.
  destruct Hfalse as [b' Hfalse].
  inversion Hfalse.
Qed.


Lemma eqdom_emp_emp_r:
  ∀ (m: M2.map)
         (Heqdom: eqdom M1.emp m),
   m = M2.emp.
Proof.
  intros.
  apply M2.extensionality.
  intros.
  destruct m.
  induction lst.


  unfold M2.get.
  simpl.
  auto.

  destruct a0.
  unfold eqdom in Heqdom.
  specialize (Heqdom a0).
  destruct Heqdom as [Heqdom1 Heqdom2].
  assert (M2.indom (M2.listset_con (lst:=(a0, b) :: lst) i) a0)
    by (
        unfold M2.indom;
        ∃ b;
               unfold M2.get; simpl;
               rewrite A.eq_beq_true; auto).
  assert (M1.indom M1.emp a0) as Hfalse by auto.
  unfold M1.indom in Hfalse.
  rewrite M1.emp_sem in Hfalse.
  destruct Hfalse as [b' Hfalse].
  inversion Hfalse.
Qed.

Lemma m1_eqdom_eqdom:
  ∀ m1 m2 m
         (Hm1eqdom: M1.eqdom m1 m2)
         (Heqdom: eqdom m1 m),
    eqdom m2 m.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold eqdom in ×.
  unfold M1.eqdom in ×.
  intros.
  specialize (Hm1eqdom x).
  specialize (Heqdom x).
  destruct Hm1eqdom as [Hm1eqdom1 Hm1eqdom2].
  destruct Heqdom as [Heqdom1 Heqdom2].
  split; auto.
Qed.

Fixpoint minus' (rl1: M1.rlist) (rl2 : M2.rlist) {struct rl1} : M1.rlist :=
  match rl1 with
    | nil ⇒ nil
    | (a,b) :: rl1' ⇒
      match (M2.get' rl2 a) with
        | Some b' ⇒ (minus' rl1' rl2)
        | None ⇒ M1.set' a b (minus' rl1' rl2)
      end
  end.

Lemma is_orderset_minus' : ∀ (rl1: M1.rlist) (rl2 : M2.rlist),
  M1.is_orderset rl1 → M1.is_orderset (minus' rl1 rl2).
Proof.
  intros rl1 rl2 Hrl1.
  induction rl1 as [|(a', b') rl1' IHrl1'].
  simpl; trivial.
  simpl in ×.
  destruct (M2.get' rl2 a').
  apply (IHrl1' (proj2 Hrl1)).
  apply M1.is_orderset_set'.
  apply (IHrl1' (proj2 Hrl1)).
Qed.

Definition minus (m : M1.map) (m1 : M2.map) : M1.map :=
  @M1.listset_con (minus' (M1.lst m) (M2.lst m1))
    (@is_orderset_minus' _ _ (M1.prf m)).

Lemma lb_minus' : ∀ (rl1: M1.rlist) (rl2 : M2.rlist) a,
  M1.lb a rl1 → M1.lb a (minus' rl1 rl2).
Proof.
  intros rl1 rl2.
  induction rl1 as [|(a', b') rl1' IHrl1'].
    intros a H.
    simpl; trivial.
  simpl in ×.
  intros a [Heq Hlb].
  destruct (M2.get' rl2 a').
  apply (IHrl1' _ Hlb).
  apply M1.lb_set'_gt; trivial.
  apply IHrl1'; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma minus_sem : ∀ (m:M1.map) (m1 : M2.map) a,
    M1.get (minus m m1) a
    = match (M1.get m a, M2.get m1 a) with
        | (Some b, Some b1) ⇒ None
        | (Some b1, None) ⇒ Some b1
        | (None, Some b2) ⇒ None
        | (None, None) ⇒ None
      end.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 a.
  unfold minus, M1.get.
  destruct m1 as [rl1 prf1].
  destruct m2 as [rl2 prf2].
  simpl.
  induction rl1 as [|(a', b') rl1' IHrl1'].

  simpl.
  destruct (M2.get (M2.listset_con (lst:=rl2) prf2) a);auto.

  unfold M2.get in ×.
  simpl in ×.
  destruct prf1 as [lbprf prf].
  destruct (M1.eq_dec a a') as [Heq | Hneq].
a = a'
  subst.
  rewrite M1.lb_notin with (rl:=rl1') in IHrl1'; auto.
  rewrite (A.eq_beq_true); auto.
  destruct (M2.get' rl2 a'); auto.
  rewrite M1.get'_set'; auto.
a <> a'
  rewrite (A.neq_beq_false); auto.
  destruct (M2.get' rl2 a'); auto.
  rewrite (M1.get'_set'_neq (minus' rl1' rl2)); auto.
Qed.

Lemma eqdom_join_partition_l:
  ∀ m1 m2 m m'
         (Heqdom: eqdom m' m)
         (Hjoin: M2.join m1 m2 m),
  ∃ m1' m2', M1.join m1' m2' m' ∧ eqdom m1' m1 ∧ eqdom m2' m2.
Proof.
  intros.
  ∃ (minus m' m2), (minus m' m1).
  split.

  unfold M1.join in ×.
  unfold eqdom in ×.
  unfold M1.indom in ×.
  unfold M2.indom in ×.
  intros.

  specialize (Heqdom a).
  repeat rewrite minus_sem.

  assert (∃ b': B2.B, None = Some b') as Hfalse
      by eauto.
  destruct Hfalse as [b' Hfalse].
  congruence.

  split.
  unfold eqdom in ×.
  unfold M1.indom in ×.
  unfold M2.indom in ×.
  unfold M2.join in ×.
  intros.
  specialize (Heqdom x).
  specialize (Hjoin x).
  split.
eqdom ->
  intros Hget.
  destruct Hget as [b Hget].
  rewrite minus_sem in Hget.
  destruct (M2.get m1 x); destruct (M2.get m2 x); destruct (M2.get m x); destruct (M1.get m' x);
    (try solve [exfalso; auto]);
    (try solve [congruence]);
    (try solve [eauto]).

  assert (∃ b: B2.B, None = Some b)
    by (apply Heqdom; eauto).
  congruence.

eqdom <-
  intros Hget.
  destruct Hget as [b Hget].
  rewrite minus_sem in ×.
  destruct (M2.get m1 x); destruct (M2.get m2 x); destruct (M2.get m x); destruct (M1.get m' x);
    (try solve [exfalso; auto]);
    (try solve [congruence]);
    (try solve [eauto]).

  assert (∃ b: B1.B, None = Some b)
    by (apply Heqdom; eauto).
  congruence.

  unfold eqdom in ×.
  unfold M1.indom in ×.
  unfold M2.indom in ×.
  unfold M2.join in ×.
  intros.
  specialize (Heqdom x).
  specialize (Hjoin x).
  split.
eqdom ->
  intros Hget.
  destruct Hget as [b Hget].
  rewrite minus_sem in Hget.
  destruct (M2.get m1 x); destruct (M2.get m2 x); destruct (M2.get m x); destruct (M1.get m' x);
    (try solve [exfalso; auto]);
    (try solve [congruence]);
    (try solve [eauto]).

  assert (∃ b: B2.B, None = Some b)
    by (apply Heqdom; eauto).
  congruence.

eqdom <-
  intros Hget.
  destruct Hget as [b Hget].
  rewrite minus_sem in ×.
  destruct (M2.get m1 x); destruct (M2.get m2 x); destruct (M2.get m x); destruct (M1.get m' x);
    (try solve [exfalso; auto]);
    (try solve [congruence]);
    (try solve [eauto]).

  assert (∃ b: B1.B, None = Some b)
    by (apply Heqdom; eauto).
  congruence.
Qed.

Fixpoint minus_l' (rl1: M2.rlist) (rl2 : M1.rlist) {struct rl1} : M2.rlist :=
  match rl1 with
    | nil ⇒ nil
    | (a,b) :: rl1' ⇒
      match (M1.get' rl2 a) with
        | Some b' ⇒ (minus_l' rl1' rl2)
        | None ⇒ M2.set' a b (minus_l' rl1' rl2)
      end
  end.

Lemma is_orderset_minus_l' : ∀ (rl1: M2.rlist) (rl2 : M1.rlist),
  M2.is_orderset rl1 → M2.is_orderset (minus_l' rl1 rl2).
Proof.
  intros rl1 rl2 Hrl1.
  induction rl1 as [|(a', b') rl1' IHrl1'].
  simpl; trivial.
  simpl in ×.
  destruct (M1.get' rl2 a').
  apply (IHrl1' (proj2 Hrl1)).
  apply M2.is_orderset_set'.
  apply (IHrl1' (proj2 Hrl1)).
Qed.

Definition minus_l (m : M2.map) (m1 : M1.map) : M2.map :=
  @M2.listset_con (minus_l' (M2.lst m) (M1.lst m1))
    (@is_orderset_minus_l' _ _ (M2.prf m)).

Lemma lb_minus_l' : ∀ (rl1: M2.rlist) (rl2 : M1.rlist) a,
  M2.lb a rl1 → M2.lb a (minus_l' rl1 rl2).
Proof.
  intros rl1 rl2.
  induction rl1 as [|(a', b') rl1' IHrl1'].
    intros a H.
    simpl; trivial.
  simpl in ×.
  intros a [Heq Hlb].
  destruct (M1.get' rl2 a').
  apply (IHrl1' _ Hlb).
  apply M2.lb_set'_gt; trivial.
  apply IHrl1'; trivial.
Qed.

Lemma minus_l_sem : ∀ (m:M2.map) (m1 : M1.map) a,
    M2.get (minus_l m m1) a
    = match (M2.get m a, M1.get m1 a) with
        | (Some b, Some b1) ⇒ None
        | (Some b1, None) ⇒ Some b1
        | (None, Some b2) ⇒ None
        | (None, None) ⇒ None
      end.
Proof.
  intros m1 m2 a.
  unfold minus_l, M2.get.
  destruct m1 as [rl1 prf1].
  destruct m2 as [rl2 prf2].
  simpl.
  induction rl1 as [|(a', b') rl1' IHrl1'].

  simpl.
  destruct (M1.get (M1.listset_con (lst:=rl2) prf2) a);auto.

  unfold M1.get in ×.
  simpl in ×.
  destruct prf1 as [lbprf prf].
  destruct (M2.eq_dec a a') as [Heq | Hneq].
a = a'
  subst.
  rewrite M2.lb_notin with (rl:=rl1') in IHrl1'; auto.
  rewrite (A.eq_beq_true); auto.
  destruct (M1.get' rl2 a'); auto.
  rewrite M2.get'_set'; auto.
a <> a'
  rewrite (A.neq_beq_false); auto.
  destruct (M1.get' rl2 a'); auto.
  rewrite (M2.get'_set'_neq (minus_l' rl1' rl2)); auto.
Qed.

Lemma eqdom_join_partition_r:
  ∀ m1 m2 m m'
         (Heqdom: eqdom m m')
         (Hjoin: M1.join m1 m2 m),
  ∃ m1' m2', M2.join m1' m2' m' ∧ eqdom m1 m1' ∧ eqdom m2 m2'.
Proof.
  intros.
  ∃ (minus_l m' m2), (minus_l m' m1).
  split.

  unfold M2.join in ×.
  unfold eqdom in ×.
  unfold M2.indom in ×.
  unfold M1.indom in ×.
  intros.
  specialize (Hjoin a).
  specialize (Heqdom a).
  repeat rewrite minus_l_sem.
  destruct (M1.get m1 a); destruct (M1.get m2 a); destruct (M1.get m a); destruct (M2.get m' a); auto.
  destruct Heqdom as [Heqdom1 Heqdom2].
  assert (∃ b': B1.B, None = Some b') as Hfalse
      by eauto.
  destruct Hfalse as [b' Hfalse].
  congruence.

  split.
  unfold eqdom in ×.
  unfold M2.indom in ×.
  unfold M1.indom in ×.
  unfold M1.join in ×.
  intros.
  specialize (Heqdom x).
  specialize (Hjoin x).
  split.
eqdom ->
  intros Hget.
  destruct Hget as [b Hget].
  rewrite minus_l_sem.
  destruct (M1.get m1 x); destruct (M1.get m2 x); destruct (M1.get m x); destruct (M2.get m' x);
    (try solve [exfalso; auto]);
    (try solve [congruence]);
    (try solve [eauto]).

  assert (∃ b: B2.B, None = Some b)
    by (apply Heqdom; eauto).
  congruence.

eqdom <-
  intros Hget.
  destruct Hget as [b Hget].
  rewrite minus_l_sem in ×.
  destruct (M1.get m1 x); destruct (M1.get m2 x); destruct (M1.get m x); destruct (M2.get m' x);
    (try solve [exfalso; auto]);
    (try solve [congruence]);
    (try solve [eauto]).

  assert (∃ b: B1.B, None = Some b)
    by (apply Heqdom; eauto).
  congruence.

  unfold eqdom in ×.
  unfold M2.indom in ×.
  unfold M1.indom in ×.
  unfold M1.join in ×.
  intros.
  specialize (Heqdom x).
  specialize (Hjoin x).
  split.
eqdom ->
  intros Hget.
  destruct Hget as [b Hget].
  rewrite minus_l_sem.
  destruct (M1.get m1 x); destruct (M1.get m2 x); destruct (M1.get m x); destruct (M2.get m' x);
    (try solve [exfalso; auto]);
    (try solve [congruence]);
    (try solve [eauto]).

  assert (∃ b: B2.B, None = Some b)
    by (apply Heqdom; eauto).
  congruence.

eqdom <-
  intros Hget.
  destruct Hget as [b Hget].
  rewrite minus_l_sem in ×.
  destruct (M1.get m1 x); destruct (M1.get m2 x); destruct (M1.get m x); destruct (M2.get m' x);
    (try solve [exfalso; auto]);
    (try solve [congruence]);
    (try solve [eauto]).

  assert (∃ b: B1.B, None = Some b)
    by (apply Heqdom; eauto).
  congruence.
Qed.

Lemma m1_eqdom_eqdom_m2_eqdom:
  ∀ m1 m2 m1' m2'
         (Hm1eqdom: M1.eqdom m1 m2)
         (Heqdom: eqdom m1 m1')
         (Heqdom': eqdom m2 m2') ,
    M2.eqdom m1' m2'.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold eqdom in ×.
  unfold M1.eqdom in ×.
  unfold M2.eqdom in ×.
  intros.
  specialize (Hm1eqdom x).
  specialize (Heqdom x).
  specialize (Heqdom' x).
  destruct Hm1eqdom as [Hm1eqdom1 Hm1eqdom2].
  destruct Heqdom as [Heqdom1 Heqdom2].
  destruct Heqdom' as [Heqdom1' Heqdom2'].
  split; auto.
Qed.

Lemma m2_eqdom_eqdom_m1_eqdom:
  ∀ m1 m2 m1' m2'
         (Hm1eqdom: M2.eqdom m1 m2)
         (Heqdom: eqdom m1' m1)
         (Heqdom': eqdom m2' m2) ,
    M1.eqdom m1' m2'.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold eqdom in ×.
  unfold M1.eqdom in ×.
  unfold M2.eqdom in ×.
  intros.
  specialize (Hm1eqdom x).
  specialize (Heqdom x).
  specialize (Heqdom' x).
  destruct Hm1eqdom as [Hm1eqdom1 Hm1eqdom2].
  destruct Heqdom as [Heqdom1 Heqdom2].
  destruct Heqdom' as [Heqdom1' Heqdom2'].
  split; auto.
Qed.

Lemma eqdom_m1_eqdom_m2_eqdom_eqdom:
  ∀ m1 m2 m1' m2'
         (Hm1eqdom: M1.eqdom m1 m1')
         (Hm2eqdom: M2.eqdom m2 m2')
         (Heqdom: eqdom m1 m2),
    eqdom m1' m2'.
Proof.
  intros.
  unfold eqdom in ×.
  unfold M1.eqdom in ×.
  unfold M2.eqdom in ×.
  intros.
  specialize (Hm1eqdom x).
  specialize (Hm2eqdom x).
  specialize (Heqdom x).
  destruct Hm1eqdom as [Hm1eqdom1 Hm1eqdom2].
  destruct Hm2eqdom as [Hm2eqdom1 Hm2eqdom2].
  destruct Heqdom as [Heqdom1 Heqdom2].
  split; auto.
Qed.
